stratcomments:
Vyazniki Assemblage; the terminal part of the Late Tatarian (terminal part of the Vyatkian) (Golubev 2000; Benton 2012, Geology).

"similarly old collection [as the type locality of Archosaurus rossicus]" (Gower & Sennikov, 2000);
"same geological age as the type locality [of Megawhaitsia patrichae]" (Ivakhnenko, 2008);
the type locality of M. patrichae and A. rossicus is Vyazniki, being Vyatkian in age
